high_descs: Turn left and move to the counter area against the wall between the loaf of bread and the pan.
Pick up the potato to the rear of the apple from the counter.
Turn right and move to the silver microwave to the right of the red toaster in the corner of the room.
Open the microwave, place the potato on the plate to the left of the mug, microwave the potato, then open the microwave, pick up the potato, and then close the microwave door.
Turn left, move towards the white door, then turn right, move to the gray pan on the counter to your right, then turn left and face the window to the right of the door.
Place the potato in the gray rubbish bin on the floor in front of the window.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato in the rubbish bin.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight slightly then turn left and face to the counter
Pick up the potato from the counter
Turn around and move forward slightly then turn left and walk straight then turn left to face the microwave
Place the potato in the microwave, heat it and then remove it from the microwave
Turn around walk straight past the kitchen island then turn right and walk to the white trash bin on the left and face it
Place the potato in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato in the microwave and place it in the trash

high_descs: Turn left, take one step, then face the left counter.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Turn around and almost to the door, then veer right to the gray trash bin.
Place the potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato in a trash bin.
